ActCanada-Ukraine Free Trade Agreement Implementation Act
SubjectOrder Fixing the Date of Entry into Force of the Free Trade Agreement between Canada and Ukraine as the Day on Which the Canada–Ukraine Free Trade Agreement Implementation Act, 2023 Comes into Force
PrecisOrder fixing the day on which the Canada–Ukraine Free Trade Agreement Implementation Act, 2023, comes into force as the day on which the CANADA - UKRAINE FREE TRADE AGREEMENT, done at Ottawa on 22 September 2023, COMES INTO FORCE.
